reviews.text:
We have a most definitively peach green tea flavor. The hibiscus and lavender mixed together beautifully,  and yet both flavors are completely distinctive. The Fuji helps to plump up the peach notes, the raspberry... this is a brilliant notion. It adds beautifully to the whole mix. The peach gummy adds texture and sweetness and the ws-23 just the right amount of chill to the whole mix.&#xD;
&#xD;
This stuff is fantastic, good anytime,  and utterly brilliant for summer.
